<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Clartalk - Debators Reward</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #0f0f0f;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.3);
    }
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: orange;
    }
    .reward-box {
      background-color: #222;
      border-left: 5px solid orange;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .reward-box h3 {
      color: orange;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .reward-box p, .reward-box ul {
      color: #ddd;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .note {
      background-color: #333;
      border-left: 5px solid orange;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #ffcc99;
    }
    .badge-img {
      width: 150px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: block;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>🔥 Clartalk Debators Reward System</h1>

    <div class="reward-box">
      <h3>1️⃣ Earn ₹3 Per View After 100 Views</h3>
      <p>Once your debate crosses <strong>100 views</strong>, you start earning ₹3 for <strong>every view</strong> including the first 100.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Example: 105 views = ₹3 × 105 = ₹315</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="reward-box">
      <h3>2️⃣ Rank in Top 10 = Special Rewards</h3>
      <p>If your debate enters the <strong>Top 10 leaderboard</strong>, you’ll earn:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🏅 Clartalk Special Badge</li>
        <li>🎁 Special Rewards and Recognition</li>
      </ul>
      <img src="/images/Clartalk-Badge.png" alt="Clartalk Special Badge" class="badge-img">
    </div>

    <div class="reward-box">
      <h3>3️⃣ Refer 5+ Debators & Earn 10% of Their Earnings</h3>
      <p>Refer at least <strong>5 debators</strong> who create debates, and you'll get:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>💰 10% of what they earn, automatically</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="reward-box">
      <h3>4️⃣ Create 5+ Debates = Get Featured & Rewarded</h3>
      <p>When you publish more than <strong>5 debates</strong> that meet the time and quality criteria:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🌟 You become a Specialized Featured Debator</li>
        <li>🎉 Receive extra rewards and spotlight on Clartalk</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      ⚠️ <strong>Note:</strong> Only real, high-quality content is rewarded. Fake views or spam activities will disqualify you. Stay original. Stay bold.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
